Other protection options For other NFC tag protection options (password) I would recommend you to use the app NFC Tools.\n\n
Lock tag info
Tap the tag to lock it permanently.\n\n
Lock tag This process will lock the tag permanently! You can still read data from it, but nothing else. Be careful with this option. \n\n Should work on most NFC tags.
Set password By setting a password only the person that knows the password can write to the tag. \n\n This only works on the NFC tag:\n NXP-NTAG213
Remove password By removing the password, you can write to the tag again. \n\n This only works on the NFC tag:\n NXP-NTAG213
Please select an option.
//ABOUT ACTIVITY About the application The app is mean to save private data like usernames, passwords, PIN numbers and other sensitive informations on a NFC tag.\n\nYou can take a standard NFC tag like the NXP-NTAG213 and use the tag to save your passwords on your desk. Only you can read the data on the tag. You can stick a tag to your wallet and save your PIN numbers and other info on it. If the wallet gets stolen, nobody but you can read the encoded data on the tag.
Development Hello, I made this app because I wanted to store my password safely on my desk. But primarily because I ordered 100+ NFC tags and I had no idea what to do with them. If you like the app you can buy me a coffee or not.
